{"tid":2041431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部：若英予香港居民永久居留　中方保留反制權利","createTime":"2020-05-29T08:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T09:01:28.000Z","uid":333,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ff7db5f5fec7ad5b9e11c8ee4f26b84e67d3c3bf","tid":2041431,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:35:32.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】在北京，外交部說如果英國給予香港居民永久居留權，中方保留對英國採取反制措施的權利。<br />\n<br />\n英國外相藍韜文較早前說，如果中國實施港區國安法，英方會延長英國國民（海外）護照，即BNO持有人的逗留期限，由免簽證入境六個月，改為容許護照持有人在英國工作及學習十二個月，長遠可以作為進一步申請公民資格的途徑。<br />\n<br />\n有關注香港事務的保守黨國會議員指，藍韜文的聲明是個好開始，但期望當局採取更多措施，包括加快BNO持有人取得英國公民資格的程序。<br />\n<br />\n在野自由民主黨則呼籲當局，將BNO持有人的權利延伸至所有香港居民。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d2549bf6405b17fabf5778aed7fae988bb26c9","tid":2041431,"uid":87039,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:37:48.000Z","msg":"點解北京唔放棄拎住BNO既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地都唔愛國"},{"pid":"7edf2d7abff20555d284bc1bda70dab8034af6fb","tid":2041431,"uid":38332,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"點解一個不容許他國干預自己內政嘅國家<br />\n但又偏偏乜都關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8cf56aabeb64b1684791353fde6e4be26fce151","tid":2041431,"uid":30215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:38:30.000Z","msg":"How<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a50924b3230fad2aa629cb06a9babe8b1e546b","tid":2041431,"uid":58852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:38:37.000Z","msg":"又話唔滿意就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b4e2ca81cac1ff88ff2ad00b7f5cfc928fdd172","tid":2041431,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:38:47.000Z","msg":"反制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a